{"tid":2059511,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"楊潤紅： 教師只能處理紅白二事才能請事假 否則教育局會嚴肅跟進","createTime":"2020-06-11T03:37:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-11T04:05:35.000Z","uid":22556,"like":3,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"8a7e8cb3c9e7f747d925d38d4f06d23fb3704325","tid":2059511,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T03:37:12.000Z","msg":"楊潤雄今早在電台節目再以反對政治帶入校園為由，重申教育局反對任何形式罷課，又指作為專業教師，不應該罷課，更聲言參與罷課並非教師申請事假的原因，教師只可以用事假處理紅白二事等緊急事務。<br />\n<br />\n楊潤雄指，教師若突然不回校教書，是紀律問題，校方作為僱主，應按學校程序及僱傭條例去處理，教育局亦會嚴肅跟進<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200611/RARXGO447AQDEJITCLXG4UHOFM/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200611%2FRARXGO447AQDEJITCLXG4UHOFM%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=zXAIbGZ2Qohx5%2Bb7%2FAbjRKooFDKVeMyzaQj0gYzwHSI%3D&h=ba7d600d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200611%2FRARXGO447AQDEJITCLXG4UHOFM%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=e9e9fae6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200611/RARXGO447AQDEJITCLXG4UHOFM/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</a>"},{"pid":"9236b1e8b29446e8a18ce8689728fecef2bbad39","tid":2059511,"uid":262389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T03:38:10.000Z","msg":"當大家仲係度內鬥嘅時候，麻煩你睇下流亡台灣嘅手足點講<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2059034\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2059034</a>"},{"pid":"21a6919ba561fc083a4e0cc43ecefde1c4c47560","tid":2059511,"uid":355064,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T03:39:47.000Z","msg":"呢個局長真係垃圾之最<br />\n孫明揚都冇佢咁垃圾"},{"pid":"ce01c47f71464528cc5a5eac023fe025e4ed7e37","tid":2059511,"uid":24036,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T03:41:20.000Z","msg":"出席楊潤雄老母 老婆再婚宴<br />\n出席楊潤雄兒子出殯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d699c12c225ccab6eb226fc0d5b53cec17bf1daf","tid":2059511,"uid":2419,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T03:47:07.000Z","msg":"香港再出殯算唔算白事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc7038a5a603ef8f9a770b18ec518ad73f61d792","tid":2059511,"uid":25424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T03:52:00.000Z","msg":"咁我為支持國安法去做義工可唔可以請假"},{"pid":"988169ae24027d9a946f4af2abe6f5ce56bd164a","tid":2059511,"uid":353256,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"dc7038a5a603ef8f9a770b18ec518ad73f61d792","tid":2059511,"uid":25424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T03:52:00.000Z","msg":"咁我為支持國安法去做義工可唔可以請假"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T03:55:40.000Z","msg":"可以<br />\n白事嚟"},{"pid":"74cedf37ff6d13f541e525fdfcd472a26e067b21","tid":2059511,"uid":237300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T04:05:35.000Z","msg":"老豆有意外入咗ICU ，我要請假去醫院睇佢，你夠膽就答我呢個係紅事定白事？"}]}